      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Maintained to the highest standards of mechanical and aesthetic excellence, every detail\u2014from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments\u2014testifies to its meticulous ownership history. This is an investment-grade example, offering unparalleled refinement and peak performance for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
